alert_support: Support importing data via Excel or JSON files.
alert_instruction: When importing, if the id is empty, new data will be created. If the id has a value, the corresponding data will be updated. The id is obtained by exporting data. Maximum 10,000 records per import.
upload_text: Click or drag files here to upload
upload_hint: Only supports: json.xlsx.csv files, please note required fields
progress_tip: Data is being imported, please do not close the page
result_subtitle_tip: You can download the failed data, modify it and re-import
